' ===========================
UC60_1 ..> UC60_2 : <<extend>>
UC60_1 ..> UC60_3 : <<extend>>
UC60_1 ..> UC60_4 : <<extend>>
UC60_6 ..> UC60_7 : <<include>>

UC61_1 ..> UC61_2 : <<include>>
UC61_1 ..> UC61_3 : <<include>>
